tm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475649-20190820.htm&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex26H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=a19801f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475649-20190820.htm&h=a308f2d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475649-20190820.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:32:54.000Z","msg":"要我停勇武成個月先考慮下個垃圾獨立調查委員會？食屎啦中央，我今個星期就勇武比你睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0b9f3aae6d4838ab2f3294df1e698453fdcc98","tid":1489700,"uid":1230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:35:54.000Z","msg":"佢唔回應 831係升級硬呀"},{"pid":"da42fbc1898ff4222d844bc1ae9426625c73f903","tid":1489700,"uid":44312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:36:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">個個都話823死線，但熱門一個post都無？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1489735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1489735</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"82e946652a64993b3134cf3a6a8ce35b672350cd","tid":1489700,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:36:33.000Z","msg":"佢安唔安心關我撚事"},{"pid":"804217d265a2f84691b61ac7d8b950397d91ed97","tid":1489700,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:36:58.000Z","msg":"ok 十一嚟送場大禮"},{"pid":"203b3383f0aefc4c9ad8c78e33057e97f9e3235d","tid":1489700,"uid":123615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:37:26.000Z","msg":"佢唔射咪無囉<br />\n佢係咪支持禁用tg<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba04006738cea5416ac21d651ed179733460c3b","tid":1489700,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:37:27.000Z","msg":"任由香港自生自滅 將香